'''Yawurute''' (izina mu [[Igiturukiya]] ''yoğurt'')

Ku bantu bafata ibyo biribwa bikomoka ku mata birimo nka [[foromaje]], yawurute, abakoreweho igenzura basanze bafite amahirwe macye yo gufatwa n’indwara z’umutima kurusha abatarigeze bafata ibyo biribwa. Umubiri ukenera kandi ibikomoka ku mata : amata, yawurute, foromaje ibi bitanga karisiyumu ikomeza amagufa , poroteyine kimwe na vitamine A,B,C.


